# how to destroy all the resources created by terraform
# how to destroy specific resourses created by terraform
# how to destroy the resources using code commit


# create resources using pratical-01 and pratical-02 files

$ terraform state list 
  aws_instance.server-1
  github_repository.example

$ terraform destroy

$ terraform destroy -target aws_instance.server-1

$ terraform destroy 


# if you want to destroy a perticular resourse, just commit the code on the code block and execute below command.
